<ul>
<li>Corset form and quilted curvy cup constructing;</li>
<li>Classic and basic technology for making corset for medium (plastic bones) and strong (steel bones) waist reduction;</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Skills you gain:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Marking bone location;</li>
<li>Sewing together curvy corset parts;</li>
<li>Sewing quilted cups;</li>
<li>Ironing and steaming the right way to form it.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Where to use:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Perfect for sewing wedding dresses with different decorations: drapery, applique, embroidery;</li>
<li>Garments made with&nbsp;this technology are suitable for any body type and size;</li>
<li>Great for reshaping silhouettes and creating proportional forms.</li>
</ul>
